1
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,840
I'm starting to wonder

2
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,880
if your aunt is hiding something.

3
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,240
Mr. Yai marrying Pinanong

4
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:31,480
is like keeping
a venomous snake by his side.

5
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:35,400
If you're sure you're not going to
betray Madam, you have to prove it.

6
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,560
Give all your dowry to me.

7
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:41,280
The security camera
you had me install really wasn't a waste.

8
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:52,360
Take this money and buy On
a top-quality diamond engagement ring.

9
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,520
Thank you, Auntie.

10
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,200
Instead of transferring,

11
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,880
we had to wait for cash.

12
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,960
So analog.

13
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,640
Miss On, we need to head back
to Bangkok now.

14
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,360
Your parents are waiting.

15
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,840
That is all, right?

16
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,480
Let's go, Na.

17
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:26,400
Auntie, I don't think
just the ring would be enough.

18
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:31,440
I'll send you
the rest of the dowry on the list later.

19
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,000
Don't worry.

20
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,560
Just you wait.

21
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,720
Once she becomes family,

22
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,640
I'll get it all back.

23
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,800
But we still have some money left.

24
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,320
How would this be enough?

25
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,240
The dowry that the lady requested…

26
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:02,120
Geez, it's enough
for their whole family to live on.

27
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,760
Come on, don't look down
on a small amount of money.

28
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:09,720
Did you forget
that we can magically multiply it?

29
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:27,080
Noi, what are you looking at?

30
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,600
Somebody, help. Pin.

31
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,800
You startled me.

32
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:32,840
Where's Mr. Yai?

33
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,960
There.

34
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,640
He's holed up in his office
and hasn't come out yet.

35
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,320
Not sure if something's going on.

36
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,480
Mr. Yai.

37
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,320
Are you not feeling well?

38
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,920
Where were you?

39
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,400
I woke up, and you were gone.

40
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,920
Thought you'd run off with someone.

41
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,760
I went to see Mom this morning.

42
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,760
What do you want to eat today?

43
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,080
I'll cook for you.

44
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:20,920
I'm concerned
about all the dowry right now.

45
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:24,120
It might not be safe to keep it at home.

46
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,680
We should keep it at the bank.

47
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,320
I'm fine with whatever you decide.

48
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,640
Here.

49
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:42,440
Can you bring it out of the safe?

50
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,160
Well? Hurry up.

51
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,120
Pin.

52
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,640
Yes?

53
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:07,040
Why are your hands freezing cold,

54
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:10,240
like a child who's getting caught
making a mistake?

55
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,720
Do you have anything to confess?

56
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:22,400
No. I don't have anything.

57
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,320
You stone-faced culprit.

58
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:28,560
If I hadn't installed a camera in here,
I'd be a fool whose wife betrayed him.

59
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,280
Camera?

60
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,480
So you were actually suspicious of me?

61
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,800
Then let's see if I was right.

62
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,800
Give it to me.

63
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:58,960
You gave all your dowry to my enemy.

64
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,680
That means you betrayed me.

65
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,880
You're misunderstanding.

66
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,640
With clear evidence,
what could I misunderstand?

67
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:35,440
Why do they have to block our way?

68
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,640
Such a bunch of uneducated hillbillies.

69
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,600
What a waste of space.

70
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,800
I'll go take a look.

71
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,400
Could you please move?

72
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,520
Hey!

73
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,280
- Hey, close the door! Close it!
- Guns.

74
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:03,880
Hey, hey, close the door!

75
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,280
- Close it right now.
- Driver, close the door. Hurry.

76
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,200
Why are they all still here?

77
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,480
You didn't take them?

78
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:21,320
I saw with my own eyes
that you used the key to open the safe.

79
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:23,480
I did open the safe,

80
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,320
but…

81
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,159
I really can't accept it.

82
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:45,000
And I know Mom wouldn't want it too.

83
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,400
Why?

84
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,080
You think it's filthy money, don't you?

85
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,320
Mom might think so.

86
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:55,400
But I believe that it's honest money
you've earned from the mine.

87
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,040
It's your hard-earned money.

88
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:59,520
Then I have the right to give it to you.

89
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,600
Have it.

90
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:05,240
But I really don't want anything from you.

91
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,880
Please keep it.

92
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,600
How about this?

93
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,240
If I'm struggling, I'll ask you for it.

94
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,080
Alright, alright.

95
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,320
Then have this diamond set.

96
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,120
Consider it a gift from me.

97
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:23,080
Don't refuse, or I'll be upset.

98
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:53,160
My mom really asked me
to give all my dowry to Madam.

99
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,040
But I couldn't do it,

100
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,200
so I just gave the diamond set
to Madam instead.

101
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,440
Why didn't you tell me?

102
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:01,360
Why did you have to act suspiciously?

103
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:04,800
I was afraid you would say I was stupid.

104
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,040
And I am really stupid.

105
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,960
Because you didn't even really want
to give the diamond set to me.

106
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,920
You were trying to use it
as bait just to test my loyalty.

107
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,280
- Pin--
- You never trust me.

108
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:20,080
In your eyes, I'm both stupid and evil.

109
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:25,400
Now that you've proved it
like you wanted to,

110
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,880
you can punish me all you want.

111
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,120
- Who were they?
- <i>I have no idea.</i>

112
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,240
It was like they were trying to rob us.

113
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,000
But once they picked up a call,

114
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:40,400
they left us here and drove off.

115
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,640
Don't tell the police.

116
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:45,000
Well, if you go to the police station,

117
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,000
you won't make it to Bangkok today.

118
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:49,680
On's parents will be waiting for too long.

119
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:52,720
Anyway, I'll hurry
and find you a new ride.

120
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,560
Yes, Auntie.

121
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,840
Krong, what are you doing?

122
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:03,160
- I'm on a roll right now.
- Hey.

123
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,040
Na was being robbed.

124
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:07,360
But they didn't take anything at all.

125
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:11,400
They might be Mr. Tong's men
who were sent to scare Na

126
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,640
to threaten us about our debt.

127
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,640
Or did he know we moved here to gamble?

128
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,480
Let's leave, then.

129
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:19,000
Right now?

130
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,520
It's a pity to lose this.

131
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:33,320
Pin. Pin, why did you lock the door?

132
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,960
Pin. Pin.

133
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:48,200
Pin. If you don't open the door,
where will I sleep tonight?

134
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,720
Yai.

135
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,600
Why did you call them to let Tatsana go?

136
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:06,240
Didn't you say you'd steal back
the money from your dowry?

137
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:08,960
But Madam Krongsuk didn't sell the dowry.

138
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:11,400
She sold the diamond set.

139
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,000
I checked with the shop.

140
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,280
It's been confirmed.

141
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,000
Here.

142
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,720
You're getting soft again, Yai.

143
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:57,840
See? She was obviously stealing.

144
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,440
It's the diamond set I gave to Pin.

145
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,840
It's her right to sell it
or give it to anyone she wants, right?

146
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:06,040
But this proves
Madam can still order Pin around.

147
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,800
She might have just wanted
to test you this time.

148
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:13,720
But what if next time
she orders Pin to do something worse?

149
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:16,000
If that happens, I won't spare even Pin.

150
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,560
I don't believe you.

151
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,880
Pan. Pan.

152
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,160
Yeah.

153
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,840
My wife's upset with me,
and my friend's being a jerk.

154
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,280
Just go, I don't care!

155
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,520
Damn it.

156
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,440
The whole farm is gossiping

157
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:39,200
that you two were getting
so lovey-dovey that the bed broke.

158
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,640
If Mr. Yai is that rough,

159
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,440
can you even handle it, sis?

160
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,080
If you're hungry,

161
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:50,720
help yourself to some of this.

162
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:52,720
Mr. Yai wouldn't come eat.

163
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:55,760
And Mom's probably at Madam's house.

164
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,160
Hey, Pin!

165
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,320
It's boiling over and starting to burn!

166
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,800
You'll burn your hand.

167
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,800
Did you burn your hand?

168
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:18,000
Pin.

169
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:21,120
What's wrong?

170
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:25,360
You just got married.

171
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:28,120
Why are you crying like this?

172
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,760
Sometimes…

173
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:41,080
I feel like I'm all alone.

174
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,400
I have no one at all.

175
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,120
Mom.

176
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:55,360
I told you
not to show your face here again.

177
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,840
Mom.

178
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:00,920
Hey.

179
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,440
Did Madam

180
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:05,360
make you hate me this much?

181
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:07,040
It's because you're
so infatuated with Yai.

182
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:10,120
You're head over heels
and can't see straight.

183
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,240
What about you?

184
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:16,840
Do you love Madam so much
that you think she's better than me?

185
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:20,800
Why would you
even compare yourself to Madam?

186
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,160
Well,

187
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:27,760
because sometimes, I feel like
you love her more than me.

188
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,120
Listen to me, Pin.

189
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,720
She isn't just our master.

190
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:35,520
She's our benefactor, our mother figure.

191
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:38,560
If you won't help her,
it's like you're abandoning me.

192
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:40,600
You never trust me.

193
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:44,800
In your eyes, I'm both stupid and evil.

194
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:02,040
I've done everything for her.

195
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,560
I love her so damn much.

196
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:08,360
There are millions of words
buried in my heart.

197
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:12,080
She should at least return the favor
by understanding me.

198
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,400
No matter what I do,
it's never good enough.

199
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,760
Nothing seems to please her.

200
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:20,600
Oh, my life.

201
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:15,920
How long are you going
to be like this, Jom?! Huh?!

202
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:19,319
As long as I want.

203
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:21,280
Until I'm bored.

204
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:23,359
You don't need to care about me.

205
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:24,640
Go.

206
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:27,240
Love and admire

207
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:31,640
your master Yai,
the thief boss, all you want!

208
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:36,040
When showing love or gratitude,

209
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:38,880
I have the wisdom
to discern right from wrong!

210
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:42,160
I don't act blindly
and stab people in the back!

211
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,080
Love?

212
00:17:45,840 --> 00:17:47,760
You're just selfish!

213
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:52,600
What happened, Uncle Win?

214
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,920
Just ask him!

215
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:57,640
What can we possibly ask from a drunk?

216
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:02,920
- Jom, do you need my help?
- Stay away from me!

217
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:04,840
Still full of pride.

218
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,320
- Help him.
- Grab his shirt.

219
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:08,480
Jom, get up.

220
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:14,320
Fancy car, head-to-toe
designer brands, but a 40-baht tip?

221
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:20,640
To my happy marriage.

222
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,400
Mr. Yai?

223
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,080
Mr. Yai's drunk?

224
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:42,160
Can I join you?

225
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:50,440
- Who are you?
- I'm…

226
00:18:51,320 --> 00:18:54,680
a fan of yours who has been
secretly admiring you, Mr. Yai.

227
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:01,640
It's my Nee, the trickster brat.

228
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:05,680
Come on, you're quite something yourself.

229
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:08,080
Mr. Yai, the hell-sent.

230
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:12,800
That's why the two of us
were born for each other.

231
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:18,560
Oppa, you're so handsome.

232
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:21,440
You check all my boxes.

233
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:30,280
Your smell's so strong.

234
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:35,320
But I brushed my teeth.

235
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,480
No, your perfume.

236
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:41,800
Your perfume is very strong.

237
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:45,360
But it's so sexy and alluring.

238
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:49,960
Mr. Yai, don't tease me.

239
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:51,640
Alright, alright.

240
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,720
Cheers.

241
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:56,400
- Cheers.
- Yeah.

242
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:07,560
Everything would be better
if you were still here.

243
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:10,280
I miss you, Uncle.

244
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,840
<i>You ignored me first, Pin.</i>

245
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:15,640
You're so jealous of me
that you had to rush to me right away?

246
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,760
I'm not.

247
00:21:19,840 --> 00:21:23,600
Well, you were about to do something
morally wrong, so I had to stop you.

248
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:27,640
I didn't sleep with Tatsanee
or do anything to her.

249
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:31,640
I'd rather sleep with my wife.

250
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:35,000
I've fallen for your trick again.

251
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:38,320
Let go. I'll go home.

252
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:39,960
Pin.

253
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:41,440
Pin.

254
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,440
Pin, what about me?

255
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,280
Let go!

256
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:49,760
You jerk!

257
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,200
Let go of me.

258
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,520
You're such a third wheel.

259
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:57,840
Why do you always have to stand in my way?

260
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,600
He was the one who texted me to come.

261
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:01,680
Someone like Mr. Yai

262
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,480
won't be influenced so easily.

263
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:05,840
You were being used as a tool
to make Pin jealous.

264
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:06,880
Remember that.

265
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:09,080
That won't bother me.

266
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:12,840
Since I'm persistent,
I'll get between them every chance I get.

267
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:15,480
Hey. Are you an escort or something?

268
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:18,120
Can't you behave
like a decent human being for once?

269
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:21,000
I don't know what
or who I need to do that for.

270
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,840
Do it for yourself.

271
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:39,280
The person I hate the most

272
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:42,160
is me, myself.

273
00:22:43,800 --> 00:22:44,800
So what?

274
00:22:45,760 --> 00:22:47,160
You want to get with me?

275
00:22:48,040 --> 00:22:49,480
I'm down to be with anything,

276
00:22:49,560 --> 00:22:52,760
people, animals, objects,
or even a disgusting fly like you.

277
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,720
You're beyond saving, huh, Tatsanee?

278
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:37,520
I was wrong to misunderstand you.

279
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,040
I'm sorry.

280
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,880
Do you remember this place?

281
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:00,960
I met you for the first time right here.

282
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,680
I fell from the tree,

283
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,160
and you tried to carry me on your back.

284
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:12,080
You liked to nap under the tree.

285
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:15,560
And I'd tease you

286
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:18,200
until you'd cry your eyes out

287
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:19,920
and run away every time.

288
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:24,440
Even once you'd grown up
a little more, you'd cry

289
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:26,560
because you thought
your mom loved Nee more.

290
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,560
You never grow up.

291
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:34,360
Wait.

292
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:39,600
I was already in college back then,

293
00:24:40,120 --> 00:24:41,600
and you weren't living here.

294
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,640
Or…

295
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:46,880
have you been back to the farm?

296
00:24:49,280 --> 00:24:50,360
I…

297
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:53,080
I was here to see Tuem.

298
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,120
I was worried about him.

299
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,080
Let's head back.

300
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:09,000
Noi will be worried.

301
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:12,760
Uh, Pin.

302
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,720
<i>I've been coming back…</i>

303
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:22,120
<i>because I missed you.</i>

304
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:33,880
Hey, who's making out over there?

305
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:37,640
I'm with my wife.

306
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,320
You have so many other paths you can take.

307
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,560
Mr. Yai. Please continue.

308
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:46,120
We wouldn't dare provoke
the groom who broke the bed.

309
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:48,240
You're our idol.

310
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:49,840
You two…

311
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,080
Those guys are so annoying.

312
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:56,600
Hey.

313
00:26:57,600 --> 00:26:59,320
It's all because of you.

314
00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:01,840
I'm so embarrassed.

315
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,200
Is the diamond beautiful, Mom?

316
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:32,440
What about

317
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:36,320
the rest of the dowry?

318
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,600
Auntie will bring the rest here later.

319
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,320
It takes time

320
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,920
because we have to find secure vehicles

321
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:49,000
and hire bodyguards we can trust.

322
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:54,040
And since we're going to have a dowry
procession, a few vans won't be enough.

323
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:16,760
Oh, right.

324
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:19,480
I've already reserved
the hotel for the wedding reception.

325
00:28:19,560 --> 00:28:24,400
And here is the figure we need
to deposit to them first.

326
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:28,560
And this is the bill
for the organizing team.

327
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:41,440
Uh, yes.

328
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,920
Krong?

329
00:29:08,880 --> 00:29:11,160
Hey, this is
the last thing of value I have.

330
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:12,320
I bought it for you.

331
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,560
Let's just invest it now.

332
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:15,840
No. You can't.

333
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,840
No.

334
00:29:17,360 --> 00:29:18,160
Hey.

335
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:20,840
It's all because of your advice.

336
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:24,040
Now we have nothing for the dowry,
and we can't even afford daily expenses.

337
00:29:24,120 --> 00:29:26,840
I told you to quit while you were ahead,
but you bet everything.

338
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,560
You…

339
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:30,360
Hey. Teera.

340
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:32,080
You dare to lay a hand on me, huh?

341
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:34,760
No, no. No, Krong. Don't.

342
00:29:51,120 --> 00:29:53,120
Stop calling me already!

343
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:57,200
Na, is that you?

344
00:29:57,720 --> 00:30:01,040
Sorry, I thought
it was a call center scam.

345
00:30:03,120 --> 00:30:04,360
How is it going?

346
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:06,120
Is everything okay on that side?

347
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,040
<i>Auntie.</i>

348
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,160
Could you please hurry?

349
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:12,160
On and her mother
already booked the hotel.

350
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,880
I need the money very soon.

351
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:18,160
How much longer
do you want me to stall for?

352
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:20,360
I've embarrassed myself long enough.

353
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:24,400
Didn't you say you've secured the money?

354
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:27,120
It's because Pin won't lend me the money.

355
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,560
This girl has forgotten her roots.

356
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:31,360
Even her own mother has been cast aside.

357
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:33,960
Before I moved into Paisal Farm,

358
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:36,480
you promised me that I'd be happy there

359
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:37,960
if I listened to you.

360
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:42,040
My wedding can't fall apart.

361
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:25,800
You… You've been
poisoning me all this time.

362
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:38,080
I… I've been so good to you.

363
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:40,880
Why are you plotting against me? Huh?

364
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:43,600
I just want this farm

365
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,160
for my son and my daughter.

366
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:48,840
What did you say?

367
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:51,360
Well, Tatsana and Tatsanee

368
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:53,440
are my children with Pha.

369
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:57,280
So Pload was right.

370
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,040
You framed him.

371
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:02,080
Not just Pload. But Yai too.

372
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:04,720
Yai didn't kill Pha.

373
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:06,280
I did it myself.

374
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,360
I did it myself, you hear me?

375
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:10,320
I did it myself.

376
00:32:12,520 --> 00:32:14,240
I killed him myself.

377
00:32:14,320 --> 00:32:16,080
You. You!

378
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,200
You!

379
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,480
You…

380
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:32,680
I could have just kept drugging you,

381
00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:35,440
but you asked for it yourself.

382
00:32:36,040 --> 00:32:37,120
But don't be scared.

383
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:41,440
Your nerves are going to die,
one by one, very slowly.

384
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:44,160
And you won't suffer at all.

385
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:55,080
Help! Help!

386
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:58,680
Help! Help!

387
00:32:59,320 --> 00:33:02,840
Help! Help!

388
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:22,760
That's my sister's cooking.

389
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:25,160
It smells so good,
I couldn't help but follow my nose.

390
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:28,080
I was just about to serve it to you.

391
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,920
Today, there's sea bass soup.

392
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:33,920
I went to the market early this morning
and bought fresh fish to braise for you.

393
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,600
Add a little bit of this,

394
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:38,120
and I think it'll taste better.

395
00:33:39,840 --> 00:33:41,440
What is this, Madam?

396
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:43,360
A magic medicine.

397
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,840
Add this in,

398
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:48,320
and tell Pin to serve the food to Yai,

399
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:51,240
since she's the only one he trusts.

400
00:33:54,120 --> 00:33:55,240
Madam.

401
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:59,120
You can't. You can't, Madam.

402
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:00,200
I can't do it.

403
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:03,560
Or do you want me
to have it instead? Fine.

404
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:05,440
You're abandoning me too
just like Pin did.

405
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:07,400
No, Madam.

406
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:09,080
Madam, please don't do it. No.

407
00:34:09,159 --> 00:34:11,679
Hello, my dear Auntie.

408
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:22,719
Oh, my. My dear nephew.

409
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:25,080
What brings you here?

410
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:28,000
Since you were my dad's beloved wife,

411
00:34:28,080 --> 00:34:30,159
I must make sure you're living well.

412
00:34:30,239 --> 00:34:33,560
Otherwise, Dad would wake up
and strangle me to death.

413
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,960
Well.

414
00:34:35,040 --> 00:34:37,719
You're such a grateful son, aren't you?

415
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,760
I'm not just being grateful to Dad.

416
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:44,840
I love my little brother too.

417
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:48,360
Yesterday, I sent my men
to protect Na and his fiancée too.

418
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:53,280
I was worried that Pin's diamond set
would be robbed on the way.

419
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:56,360
Pin's diamond set?

420
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,920
What does that have to do with Na?

421
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:03,520
Because she's my most beloved wife,
I forgave her.

422
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:07,800
But if any fly bothers
my most beloved wife again…

423
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:17,360
Don't say I didn't warn you.

424
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:31,440
Madam.

425
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:34,880
Did you see that?

426
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:37,560
He wanted to kill me and kill Na.

427
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,080
Jom.

428
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,720
Where are you going?

429
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:01,400
I'm here to say goodbye to you. I've quit.

430
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,720
But there's something important
I need to tell you first.

431
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:07,440
What is it?

432
00:36:10,680 --> 00:36:12,120
Nee.

433
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:15,320
Where should we continue the fun tonight?

434
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:18,200
What about this cabin?

435
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:20,360
It happens to be vacant.

436
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:23,840
Mr. Yai. Walk properly, will you?

437
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:27,040
Then let's celebrate until dawn,
just the two of us!

438
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:32,200
Of course. I guarantee
you won't be sleeping tonight.

439
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,800
It's true, Un.

440
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:49,040
Mr. Yai got me drunk
and forced himself on me.

441
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:52,440
You wouldn't believe

442
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:54,600
how perverted he is.

443
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:57,160
He bit me and assaulted me.

444
00:36:57,240 --> 00:37:00,520
Here, my body is all bruised.

445
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,360
I really don't understand

446
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,680
how you could be such a cruel mother

447
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:09,040
and let Pin marry Mr. Yai

448
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:11,280
when he's such a pervert.

449
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,200
Noi.

450
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:30,800
- Yes?
- Where's Pin?

451
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:34,800
Jom is leaving the farm,
so Pin is rushing to see him.

452
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:39,920
Mr. Yai?

453
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:20,920
Yai!

454
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,000
Pin. Pin.

455
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,120
Pin.

456
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,080
Jom!

457
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:41,840
Come here.

458
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:44,000
You almost hit my wife.

459
00:38:44,080 --> 00:38:44,960
Take this.

460
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,120
Yai!

461
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,600
Don't think I don't know what you did!

462
00:38:50,680 --> 00:38:51,680
- Stop!
- What the hell?

463
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:53,080
Mr. Yai, stop! Stop!

464
00:38:54,040 --> 00:38:55,240
Mr. Yai.

465
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:56,800
Jom.

466
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:03,160
He had an affair with Ms. Nee!

467
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:04,320
I saw it with my own eyes.

468
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:07,960
You bastard!

469
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:10,400
You have a wife,
but you're still sleeping around!

470
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,920
Mom!

471
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:18,080
Mr. Yai didn't sleep with Ms. Nee.

472
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:20,360
Jom is ruining my marriage.

473
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:21,520
That's not true!

474
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:24,840
Ms. Nee told me herself
that he violated her!

475
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:27,760
What I did is nothing
compared to what your Madam has done.

476
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:30,040
Not only did she have
an affair with Pha in the barn,

477
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:32,000
but she's also been
sneaking around with Teera.

478
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:34,200
It's too graphic for me to describe!

479
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:38,120
You bastard!
How could you insult Madam like that?!

480
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,920
- You'll rot in hell and never be reborn!
- Mom.

481
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:43,360
- You bastard!
- Yeah, hit me!

482
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:45,120
You're no different than my father!

483
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:46,520
You value filth over your own kin!

484
00:39:46,600 --> 00:39:47,960
Mom, stop.

485
00:39:48,040 --> 00:39:49,040
Aunt Un, calm down.

486
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:54,520
Calm down, Aunt Un. Aunt Un.

487
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:56,880
Aunt Un.

488
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:04,560
What I said about your Madam
having an affair with Pha was true.

489
00:40:07,080 --> 00:40:10,800
And don't tell me you don't know
about Madam Krongsuk and Teera.

490
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:14,480
I know about that, because I saw them.

491
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:17,720
But I won't comment
about what happened in the past.

492
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:20,400
Just messing around with Teera is enough.

493
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:23,200
Why won't you tell your mom,
so she can finally open her eyes?

494
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:25,920
I think she's been suspicious about it

495
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:28,160
but didn't want to accept it.

496
00:40:28,240 --> 00:40:30,400
She loves and respects Madam so much.

497
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:34,920
Honestly, I've never feared
Madam Krongsuk.

498
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,800
But your mom is a serious problem.

499
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:39,160
I'll send her to live somewhere else.

500
00:40:39,240 --> 00:40:41,120
Let's find her a decent house.

501
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:43,120
Send her money every month.

502
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,520
How is she supposed to live alone?

503
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:48,960
If you send her away, I'll go with her.

504
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:52,920
So am I supposed to sleep with Tuem?

505
00:40:57,320 --> 00:41:00,400
That's no good, and this isn't working.

506
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:02,760
Alright, forget it.

507
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,880
Don't wait for me tonight.

508
00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:13,640
Pin.

509
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:17,640
I have never seen Mr. Yai that upset.

510
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:20,880
Pin, why didn't you stop him?

511
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:24,040
Mr. Yai is hot-headed.

512
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:25,880
I need to wait for him to calm down.

513
00:42:05,480 --> 00:42:06,520
- Let go!
- Calm down.

514
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:08,080
Take this!

515
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:09,040
Hey.

516
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,720
Let go of me!

517
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:12,880
Please calm down.

518
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:19,600
How am I supposed to stop them? Oh, no.

519
00:42:19,680 --> 00:42:21,280
- Calm down.
- Oh, oh.

520
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,840
- Whoa, calm down.
- Hey, hey.

521
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:25,120
- Calm down!
- Hey.

522
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:26,840
- Enough.
- Stop, stop.

523
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:28,760
Please hold your girlfriend back now.

524
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:31,440
- Ma'am, please calm down.
- Please calm down.

525
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,040
- Hey.
- Calm down.

526
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:35,960
You'd doing that right in front of me?

527
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:38,800
Fight all you want.

528
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:39,960
I'm out.

529
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,920
Sir, please get involved a little.

530
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,280
He's out?

531
00:42:44,040 --> 00:42:45,720
Really? Hey.

532
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:48,240
You're dead!

533
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:51,080
Stop.

534
00:42:52,040 --> 00:42:53,760
Are you crazy? Why are you slapping me?!

535
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,440
Go take it out on your boyfriend!

536
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,920
Please calm down.

537
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,840
You!

538
00:43:02,400 --> 00:43:04,160
You'll see what Tatsanee can do.

539
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:07,320
- Hey.
- You don't know who the big shot is here?

540
00:43:08,880 --> 00:43:10,240
- Hey!
- Please.

541
00:43:10,320 --> 00:43:12,480
Piak, stop her! Stop right now!

542
00:43:12,560 --> 00:43:14,400
- Stop.
- Calm down.

543
00:43:14,480 --> 00:43:15,360
Pan!

544
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:16,640
- Stop!
- Let go!

545
00:43:16,720 --> 00:43:18,720
- Let me go!
- Hey. No.

546
00:43:21,280 --> 00:43:22,840
Please calm down.

547
00:43:23,360 --> 00:43:24,880
You shameless bitch.

548
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:26,680
You were flirting with my man.

549
00:43:26,760 --> 00:43:27,880
You'll see.

550
00:43:27,960 --> 00:43:29,520
I'll post on social media

551
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:31,640
that this farm sells something extra.

552
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:33,040
Oh, really?

553
00:43:33,120 --> 00:43:35,560
That's because a free thing like you
is old and rotten,

554
00:43:35,640 --> 00:43:37,480
so your boyfriend
doesn't want you anymore.

555
00:43:37,560 --> 00:43:40,000
- Shut your mouth! Stop.
- What?!

556
00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:42,720
- Please calm down.
- Ma'am, I'm so sorry.

557
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:46,160
It's my fault
for not training the staff well enough.

558
00:43:46,680 --> 00:43:47,480
Let go!

559
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:50,720
our farm is willing to compensate you,
and we won't charge you for damages…

560
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:52,600
Why do we have to compensate?

561
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:53,600
Quiet!

562
00:43:54,280 --> 00:43:57,200
We'll compensate you
and won't charge you for your stay.

563
00:43:59,560 --> 00:44:02,320
Fine. If you don't want
to go out of business,

564
00:44:02,400 --> 00:44:03,960
you'd better fire this bitch.

565
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:06,640
Yes. I'm so sorry.

566
00:44:06,720 --> 00:44:08,600
Oh? Where are you going?!

567
00:44:08,680 --> 00:44:11,040
- Walking away? Come back here!
- Stop it!

568
00:44:11,120 --> 00:44:14,080
Hey, I told you to do your job properly

569
00:44:14,160 --> 00:44:15,920
so you can behave normally like others.

570
00:44:16,440 --> 00:44:20,040
But you chose to get into a stupid fight
and ruin the farm's reputation?

571
00:44:21,960 --> 00:44:24,200
You're even more useless
than this grass and dirt.

572
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:26,680
I already told you I can't work.

573
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:28,680
I'm only good at hitting on boys.

574
00:44:29,240 --> 00:44:30,160
But you wouldn't listen.

575
00:44:30,240 --> 00:44:31,520
That can't be helped!

576
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,040
Damn it!

577
00:44:35,600 --> 00:44:36,960
What a crazy woman.

578
00:44:37,040 --> 00:44:38,560
I've never seen someone like this.

579
00:44:40,720 --> 00:44:41,880
Manager.

580
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:44,680
I think Ms. Nee's quite pitiful.

581
00:44:46,280 --> 00:44:47,200
Why?

582
00:44:47,800 --> 00:44:49,720
Did she flirt with you too, Piak?

583
00:44:49,800 --> 00:44:51,240
No, she didn't.

584
00:44:51,320 --> 00:44:54,160
If that were the case,
Waan wouldn't let me live.

585
00:44:55,240 --> 00:44:57,720
Well, this time,

586
00:44:58,400 --> 00:44:59,800
it wasn't Ms. Nee's fault.

587
00:45:03,600 --> 00:45:04,480
Excuse me.

588
00:45:06,480 --> 00:45:08,760
<i>Add five drops to his food daily,</i>

589
00:45:08,840 --> 00:45:10,960
<i>and he'll soon suffer heart failure.</i>

590
00:45:11,040 --> 00:45:12,360
<i>No matter how skilled the doctor is,</i>

591
00:45:12,440 --> 00:45:13,840
<i>they won't be able to detect poison.</i>

592
00:45:13,920 --> 00:45:15,400
Mr. Yai, don't eat yet.

593
00:45:15,480 --> 00:45:16,520
Please wait for me.

594
00:45:19,360 --> 00:45:20,880
<i>Pin. I was so blind.</i>

595
00:45:20,960 --> 00:45:21,760
<i>I chose the wrong woman.</i>

596
00:45:21,840 --> 00:45:23,840
<i>Let's give us another chance. Please, Pin.</i>

597
00:45:23,920 --> 00:45:25,400
- Mr. Na, let me go.
<i>- Run.</i>

598
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:28,040
You aren't strong enough
to carry me, Pin. Go.

599
00:45:28,120 --> 00:45:29,040
Go…

600
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:13,240
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul
